node.text: @alexander_road notice me
Stupidity has no cure

Nigel Pang Yew Ming, 17, who is accused of drinking from juice bottles before returning them to a supermarket shelf had his guilty plea rejected on Friday (May 22) after he maintained that he did not consent to the caption "how to spread Wuhan virus".⁣
⁣
His friend Quek Xuan Zhi, also 17, is accused of filming the incident and posting it on Instagram.⁣
⁣
The video was captioned "how to spread Wuhan virus" and was posted to an account with at least 1,360 followers.
⁣
